{"tid":1534744,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如果唔敢跳閘，就用2蚊八達通啦；如果唔敢佔領機場，就青衣東涌機鐵線，做唔到前線，唔代表無野做架。","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:03:38.000Z","uid":79553,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb7d4d37f4b7a9f23f012a3104c784009ae1878","tid":1534744,"uid":79553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"我知大家唔係好有勇氣，可能仲好廢，為左份工，始終要做狗。<br />\n<br />\n但唔好因為咁樣而放棄呢個世界，盡力做多少少，唔敢跳閘，就用2蚊八達通，唔可以令港鐵付出代價，都留返錢來捐比星火；唔敢佔領機場，咪搭多少少地鐵巴士，令到機場交通負擔增大。<br />\n<br />\n仲有罷買，罷食，罷消費。做下鍵盤戰士。出下去遊下車河。<br />\n<br />\n唔可以出100%既力，唔代表你所做既野無用。<br />\n<br />\n唔係要大家企到一樣咁前，但我始終希望，前線向後望果陣，能夠見到大家。<br />\n<br />\n同福總要同禍，難過結伴跨過。維港維繫你和我，亂世之中分對錯。<br />\n<br />\n應承我，如果世界注定燃燒，我地都會陪呢班後生仔女，走到最後。"},{"pid":"2268c68a08433c1c71a19285e22c9784f38315df","tid":1534744,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0631a12f75f443e34c1bd76d5773174f5b22f55","tid":1534744,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f07f406ae7c2215648691f40e66ef055b6a11df","tid":1534744,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062ee2c744e4abed36235be8775428de6d1bda0e","tid":1534744,"uid":312242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"老人 1.9$ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aaf8b4050c0c5392e7e5686ebf6445e90af3327","tid":1534744,"uid":143699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:04:33.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFDBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=ebd1c1ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"340aa22ca57f8e672d1e0e0096b1afece1d20083","tid":1534744,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立即普選 否則攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"aef6e746c52d55378b684033815ff9a97c58e10a","tid":1534744,"uid":79553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"講真，前線唔會因為你地唔敢沖，唔敢佔而嬲，但絕對會因為分化，唔做野而失望。<br />\n<br />\n和理非唔緊要架，但唔好QUIT GAME"},{"pid":"f407c9d39084ed4e078ce0214c141eb626134058","tid":1534744,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31d39821ced0d7f0e22853fd6f80a785fb6bf2d0","tid":1534744,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"2蚊咪都係政府補返<br />\n跳閘/唔搭最實際"},{"pid":"cb36bfe93b7a29280b402c5d78374d38968b979c","tid":1534744,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:14:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c0663b40ae5c2635e3fca386805fd8ce6d91316","tid":1534744,"uid":79553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31d39821ced0d7f0e22853fd6f80a785fb6bf2d0","tid":1534744,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:14:11.000Z","msg":"2蚊咪都係政府補返<br />\n跳閘/唔搭最實際"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"唔可能要打工仔唔搭，加上普遍打工仔都淆底，咁不如叫佢留返D車費捐星火，唔可以令狗鐵蝕，至少我地呢邊唔會蝕比狗鐵先"},{"pid":"6242cebe595e9dc00ceb85802374a7e0af378cff","tid":1534744,"uid":292730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:21:47.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"67238f3030b3e1f28479980346f6feb7bf76e5bf","tid":1534744,"uid":150544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"我完全擺黨鐵"},{"pid":"b6854a3d55252448a369049048c917cad8c66046","tid":1534744,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc357f3b193f6f8b31ab866f2aa70db726823a53","tid":1534744,"uid":79553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"記住做到幾多得幾多，但做唔到既，唔好阻人做"},{"pid":"ba1dc9fbcc45a4fd76bd831dce661e764dc6165f","tid":1534744,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"之前已經有地鐵職員出黎講過<br />\n最多罰500<br />\n就算上庭都係罰5000<br />\n<br />\n當你中產有大有細有份荀工，前線玩唔起<br />\n問下自己，你會唔會500都畀唔起？"},{"pid":"30a22339e612f68fb9b167298784cd61c5e459fe","tid":1534744,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba1dc9fbcc45a4fd76bd831dce661e764dc6165f","tid":1534744,"uid":262737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:34:02.000Z","msg":"之前已經有地鐵職員出黎講過<br />\n最多罰500<br />\n就算上庭都係罰5000<br />\n<br />\n當你中產有大有細有份荀工，前線玩唔起<br />\n問下自己，你會唔會500都畀唔起？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:34:22.000Z","msg":"講緊跳閘"},{"pid":"4a86bcc3b0ad99b7cf3daa13849428c4aaaa7490","tid":1534744,"uid":167277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n和理非都好多野可以做"},{"pid":"cb1926ca98f406b9d7f92ef4a0680ebfa4cd7c92","tid":1534744,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9658e95fae482d99ccb2f3afa2dcfa9da00b99a","tid":1534744,"uid":90204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"我係門口都諗咗五分鐘。。但一衝過去個感覺好爽 <br />\n仲有幾個學生讚我<br />\n我都見到佢地2-3個人一齊過機<br />\n各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3c36640b6a4511e3c3cd5b9671882bdd6cc820","tid":1534744,"uid":75777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"零成本罷工法！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有冇和理非熱愛搭黨鐵?"},{"pid":"45c15cfd4ded0e134428145b3981b22c799296b0","tid":1534744,"uid":79553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9658e95fae482d99ccb2f3afa2dcfa9da00b99a","tid":1534744,"uid":90204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"我係門口都諗咗五分鐘。。但一衝過去個感覺好爽 <br />\n仲有幾個學生讚我<br />\n我都見到佢地2-3個人一齊過機<br />\n各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:42:59.000Z","msg":"香港係好多乖寶寶，成日覺得罰錢都會整花佢人生咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e9abc2b55d1648aef4f4c4bfa1a6d58a72c899","tid":1534744,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14c0d3e27f639129ed02b6764d954f0f03e946b","tid":1534744,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:02:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ksEXTuP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FksEXTuP.png&h=d9a8b7a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiNeVHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiNeVHM.jpg&h=291d67fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLQ0Rf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLQ0Rf6.jpg&h=3eaacda5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phRGAHN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FphRGAHN.jpg&h=ec37db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xm2B82O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXm2B82O.jpg&h=f55b293f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}